Package com.github.treescrub.spedran.data

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.treescrub.spedran.data.Resource
      • com.github.treescrub.spedran.data.IdentifiableResource
        • com.github.treescrub.spedran.data.Game
  • public class Game
extends IdentifiableResource
    A game which has a leaderboard on SRC.

    This class is immutable and thread-safe.
